APPEARANCE.name: Fuwante (Sayaka Francois Joy to Mai Francois Joy)

description:
http://anidb.net/ch11588 [Hikari] is a 10-year-old girl that wants to be a top coordinator just like http://anidb.net/ch24152 [her mother]. She receives her starting Pokmon, http://anidb.net/ch24156 [Pochama], after saving it from an http://anidb.net/ch550 [Ariados]`s attack. Meanwhile, after conquering the Battle Frontier and motivated by his old rival http://anidb.net/ch22301 [Shigeru], http://anidb.net/ch6693 [Satoshi] sets off to the far away land of Shin`ou. Once there, he meets Hikari and is reunited by his old friend http://anidb.net/ch16390 [Takeshi]. Hikari, aiming to be top coordinator, and Satoshi, aiming to be a Pokmon Master and battle in the Sinnoh League, venture in the land of Shin`ou. Along the way, they meet lots of new Pocket Monsters, Pokmon for short.
Source: ANN (edited)
